-- action_catalog_0637 | group=community | surface=comment hubs | prompt=Which publications are good candidates for a people-also-read sidebar? | filter_note=only rows where comment_count >= 1 when the metric depends on discussion | ranking_note=default sort should stay descending by the main score with a stable domain tiebreaker | ux_note=staying useful even when comments tables are still sparse | sql=SELECT domain, name, comment_count, distinct_commenters, reply_ratio FROM ui_publication_directory ORDER BY comment_count DESC, distinct_commenters DESC, reply_ratio DESC LIMIT 25;
